<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/mycokeys.71.55493.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Dictyoarthrinium sacchari (MFLU 20 - 0439) a conidia on the host b developmental stage of terminal conidium attached to the conidiophore c-f Conidiophores and conidia (e, with distinct mother cell) g, h mature conidiophores with four-celled terminal conidium i conidiophore with two celled terminal conidium j developmental stages of conidia on conidiophore k colony on PDA after 21 days l-q conidia. Scale bars: a = 1000 μm (a); 20 μm (b, j); 50 μm (c-i); 5 μm (l-q)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/439498" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

